<p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">中国南方大多数地区以腊月二十四为“小年”，中国北方大多数地区以腊月二十三为“小年”。</span></p><p style="text-align: center;"><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://localhost:20829/upload/img/imgQuality_1/20240305/1709648451125078967.jpg" title="1709648451125078967.jpg" alt="acaee53828f84986e4842710ef9d0fba.jpg" width="318" height="228" style="width: 318px; height: 228px;"/></span></p><p><span style="color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-family: 宋体, SimSun; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1px; text-align: justify; text-indent: 28px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">小年这天，人们“祭灶”以回顾旧岁得失，反映他们“衣食有余”的梦想追求；“洒扫”以清旧尘迎新年，表达他们辞旧迎新、迎祥纳福的愿望。</span></p>